Hello Graham,

I would say this is our most likely OOTB solution.



The FS_ShareAUDIT is to target shares and it will output Users with permissions. 
The FS_TrusteePermissions is where you pick Users/Groups and then it outputs effective access.

With Either you could customize report output to filter out what you don't want.
Or you could look at the analysis and create your own custom based on it.

Definitely something we could look into.

Thanks,

Nicholas Zimmer
